de.saxsys.mvvmfx.utils.itemlist

Class ListTransformation<SourceType,TargetType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.saxsys.mvvmfx.utils.itemlist.ListTransformation<SourceType,TargetType>
  • Type Parameters:
    SourceType - the generic type of the source list.
    TargetType - the generic type of the target list.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ItemList

    public class ListTransformation<SourceType,TargetType>
extends Object
    Binds an ObservableList that contains elements of TargetType to another ObservableList that contains elements of SourceType. This is different to the normal list binding offered by JavaFX where the lists have to contain elements of the same type.
